snippet.title: VOIN – New Demo Dev Diary | tinyBuild Connect 2024
snippet.description:
Play the Demo on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2464530/VOIN/

VOIN just got a new demo and Nikita Sozidar, the solo developer behind the game, is here with the development update!
